      *
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       INICIO.
      *
       INC-OP0.
           OPEN I-O CADBIKE
           IF ST-ERRO NOT = "00"
               IF ST-ERRO = "30"
                   OPEN OUTPUT CADBIKE
                   MOVE "* CRIANDO O ARQUIVO CADBIKE.DAT *" TO MENS
                   PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
                   CLOSE CADBIKE
                   GO TO INC-OP0
                ELSE
                    MOVE "* ERRO AO ABRIR O ARQUIVO CADBIKE *" TO MENS
                    PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
                    GO TO ROT-FIM
                ELSE
                    NEXT SENTENCE.
       INC-001.
           MOVE ZEROS TO NUM-BIKE ARO VALCOMPRA VALLOC VALHORA COR
           MOVE ZEROS TO DATCOMPRA-BIKE DATULTUSO-BIKE ANOCOMPRA-BIKE
           MOVE ZEROS TO MESCOMPRA-BIKE DIACOMPRA-BIKE WNUMERO
           MOVE ZEROS TO ANOULTUSO-BIKE MESULTUSO-BIKE DIAULTUSO-BIKE
      *
           MOVE SPACES TO MARCA-BIKE MODELO-BIKE CATEG
           MOVE SPACES TO CORDESC SITUAC SITUACDESC
      *
           DISPLAY TELABIKE.
       INC-002.
           ACCEPT TNUMERO
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02 OR 01
               CLOSE CADBIKE
               GO TO ROT-FIM.
           IF WNUMERO = ZEROS
               MOVE "* CODIGO INVALIDO! *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-002.
           MOVE WNUMERO TO NUM-BIKE.
      * VALIDA A EXISTENCIA DO REGISTRO
       LER-BIKE.
           MOVE 0 TO W-SEL
           READ CADBIKE
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF ST-ERRO NOT = "23"
               IF ST-ERRO = "00"
                   DISPLAY TELABIKE
                   MOVE "* BIKE JA CADASTRADA *" TO MENS
                   PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
                   MOVE 1 TO W-SEL
                   GO TO ACE-001
               ELSE
                   MOVE "* ERRO AO LER REGISTRO *" TO MENS
                   PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
                   GO TO ROT-FIM
           ELSE
               NEXT SENTENCE.
           IF W-ACT = 01
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * NESTA LABEL O PROGRAMA COMEÃ‡A A LEITURA DOS CAMPOS
      * A PARTIR DA MARCA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       INC-003.
           ACCEPT TMARCA
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-001.
           IF MARCA-BIKE = SPACES
               MOVE "* MARCA VAZIA! *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-003.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-004.
           ACCEPT TMODELO
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-003.
           IF MODELO-BIKE = SPACES
               MOVE "* MODELO VAZIO! *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-004.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-005.
           ACCEPT TCATEG
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-004.
           IF CATEG = SPACES
               MOVE "* CATEGORIA VAZIA! *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-005.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-006.
           ACCEPT  TARO
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-005.
           IF ARO = ZEROS
               MOVE "* ARO VAZIO! *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-006.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-007.
           ACCEPT TCOR
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-006.
           IF COR = ZEROS
               MOVE "* PREENCHA A COR DE COM 1~9 *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-007.
           MOVE TABCOR(COR) TO CORDESC
           DISPLAY TCORDESC.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-008.
           ACCEPT TVALCOMPRA
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-007.
           IF VALCOMPRA = SPACES
               MOVE "* VALOR DA COMPRA NAO PODE SER ZERO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-008.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-009.
           ACCEPT TVALHORA
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-008.
           IF VALHORA = ZEROS
               MOVE "* VALOR DA HORA NAO PODE SER ZERO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-009.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-010.
           ACCEPT TVALLOC
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-009.
           IF VALLOC = ZEROS
               MOVE "* VALOR DA LOCACAO NAO PODE SER ZERO *"
                                                   TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-010.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-011.
           ACCEPT TDATCOMPRA
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-010.
           IF DATCOMPRA-BIKE = ZEROS
               MOVE "* DATA INVALIDA *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-011.
           GO TO VALDATCOMPRA.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LABEL QUE SERA ACESSADA CASO A DATA SEJA VALIDA
      * PARA A DATA DE COMPRA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       INC-011FIM.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-012.
           ACCEPT TDATULTUSO
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-011.
           IF DATULTUSO-BIKE = ZEROS
               MOVE "* DATA INVALIDA *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-012.
           GO TO VALDATULTUSO.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * LABEL QUE SERA ACESSADA CASO A DATA SEJA VALIDA
      * PARA A DATA DE ULTIMO USO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       INC-012FIM.
      *    NEXT SENTENCE
      
       INC-013.
           ACCEPT TSITUAC
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-012.
           IF SITUAC = SPACES
               MOVE "* TODA BICICLETA TEM SITUACAO! *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-013.
      * SITUACAO
           IF SITUAC = 'A' OR 'a'
               MOVE TABSITUAC(1) TO SITUACDESC
           ELSE IF SITUAC = 'D' OR 'd'
               MOVE TABSITUAC(2) TO SITUACDESC
           ELSE IF SITUAC = 'M' OR 'm'
               MOVE TABSITUAC(3) TO SITUACDESC
           ELSE IF SITUAC = 'L' OR 'l'
               MOVE TABSITUAC(4) TO SITUACDESC
           ELSE IF SITUAC = 'R' OR 'r'
               MOVE TABSITUAC(5) TO SITUACDESC
           ELSE IF SITUAC = 'B' OR 'b'
               MOVE TABSITUAC(6) TO SITUACDESC
           ELSE
               MOVE "* STATUS INVALIDO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-013.
           DISPLAY TSITUACDESC.
           IF W-SEL = 1
               GO TO ALT-OPC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * O FIM DO INPUT DE DADOS DO USUARIO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
      ***************************************************************
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * O INICIO DA GRAVACAO DE DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       INC-OPC.
           MOVE "S" TO W-OPCAO
           DISPLAY (24, 40) "DADOS OK (S/N) : ".
           ACCEPT (24, 57) W-OPCAO WITH UPDATE
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-013.
           IF W-OPCAO = "N" OR "n"
              MOVE "* DADOS RECUSADOS PELO USUARIO *" TO MENS
              PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
              GO TO INC-001.
           IF W-OPCAO NOT = "S" AND "s"
              MOVE "* DIGITE APENAS S=SIM e N=NAO *" TO MENS
              PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
              GO TO INC-OPC.
       INC-WR1.
           WRITE REGBIKE
           IF ST-ERRO = "00" OR "02"
               MOVE "* DADOS GRAVADOS *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-001.
           IF ST-ERRO = "22"
               MOVE "* BIKE JA EXISTE *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-002
           ELSE
               MOVE "* ERRO AO GRAVAR REGISTRO *" TO MENS 
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO ROT-FIM.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * ROTINA DE CONSULTA/ALTERACAO/EXCLUSAO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       ACE-001.
           DISPLAY (24, 12)
               "F1=NOVO REGISTRO   F2=ALTERAR   F3=EXCLUIR"
           ACCEPT (24, 55) W-OPCAO
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT NOT = 02 AND W-ACT NOT = 03 AND W-ACT NOT = 04
               GO TO ACE-001.
           MOVE SPACES TO MENS
           DISPLAY (24, 12) MENS
           IF W-ACT = 02
               MOVE 02 TO W-SEL
               GO TO INC-001.
           IF W-ACT = 03
               GO TO INC-003.
           IF W-ACT = 04
               GO TO EXC-OPC.
       EXC-OPC.
           DISPLAY (24, 40) "EXCLUIR   (S/N) : ".
           ACCEPT (24, 57) W-OPCAO
           IF W-OPCAO = "N" OR "n"
               MOVE "* REGISTRO NAO EXCLUIDO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-001.
           IF W-OPCAO NOT = "S" AND "s"
               MOVE "* DIGITE APENAS S=SIM  e  N=NAO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO EXC-OPC.
       EXC-DL1.
           DELETE CADBIKE RECORD
           IF ST-ERRO = "00"
               MOVE "* REGISTRO EXCLUIDO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-001.
           MOVE "* ERRO NA EXCLUSAO DO REGISTRO *" TO MENS
           PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
           GO TO ROT-FIM.
       ALT-OPC.
           DISPLAY (24, 40) "ALTERAR  (S/N) : ".
           ACCEPT (24, 57) W-OPCAO
           ACCEPT W-ACT FROM ESCAPE KEY
           IF W-ACT = 02
               GO TO INC-012.
           IF W-OPCAO = "N" OR "n"
               MOVE "* INFORMACOES NAO ALTERADAS *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-013.
           IF W-OPCAO NOT = "S" AND "s"
               MOVE "* DIGITE APENAS S=SIM  e  N=NAO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO ALT-OPC.
       ALT-RW1.
           REWRITE REGBIKE
           IF ST-ERRO = "00" OR "02"
               MOVE "* REGISTRO ALTERADO *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-001.
           MOVE "* ERRO AO ALTERAR REGISTRO *" TO MENS
           PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
           GO TO ROT-FIM.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * ROTINA DE FIM
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       ROT-FIM.
           DISPLAY (01, 01) ERASE
           EXIT PROGRAM.
       ROT-FIMP.
           EXIT PROGRAM.
       ROT-FIMS.
           STOP RUN.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * ROTINA DE MENSAGEM
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       ROT-MENS.
           MOVE ZEROS TO W-CONT.
       ROT-MENS1.
           DISPLAY (24, 12) MENS.
       ROT-MENS2.
           ADD 1 TO W-CONT
           IF W-CONT < 1000
               GO TO ROT-MENS2
           ELSE
               DISPLAY (24, 12) LIMPA.
       ROT-MENS-FIM.
           EXIT.
       ROT-ALFA-FIM.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *     VALIDACAO DAS DUAS DATAS (COMPRA E ULTIMO USO)
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
      * VALIDACAO DAS DUAS DATAS
      *
       VALDATCOMPRA.
           MOVE 1 TO WFLAGDAT
           MOVE DIACOMPRA-BIKE TO WDIA
           MOVE MESCOMPRA-BIKE TO WMES
           MOVE ANOCOMPRA-BIKE TO WANO
           GO TO VALIDARMES.
      *
       VALDATULTUSO.
           MOVE 2 TO WFLAGDAT
           MOVE DIAULTUSO-BIKE TO WDIA
           MOVE MESULTUSO-BIKE TO WMES
           MOVE ANOULTUSO-BIKE TO WANO
           GO TO VALIDARMES.
      *
       VALIDARMES.
           IF WMES > 12 OR WMES < 1
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-ERRO
           ELSE
               GO TO MESVAL.
       MESVAL.
            GO TO D31 FEV D31 D30 D31 D30 D31 D31 D30 D31 D30 D31
               DEPENDING ON WMES.
       D31.
           IF WDIA > 31 OR WDIA < 1
               MOVE ZEROS TO DATCOMPRA-BIKE
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-ERRO
           ELSE
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-FIM.
       D30.
           IF WDIA > 30 OR WDIA < 1
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-ERRO
           ELSE
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-FIM.
      * MES DE FEVEREIRO SEGUNDO CALENDARIO GREGORIANO
      * ANOS BISSEXTOS SAO RELEVANTES
       FEV.
           GO TO DIV4.
      * DIVIDIR O ANO POR 4 O RESTO PODE SER >= 0 PARA SER BISSEXTO
       DIV4.
           DIVIDE WANO BY 4 GIVING WRESTO REMAINDER WRESTO
               IF WRESTO = ZEROS
                   GO TO DIV100
               ELSE
                   GO TO DIV400.
      * DIVIDIR O ANO POR 100 O RESTO NAO PODE SER 0 PARA SER BISSEXTO
       DIV100.
           DIVIDE WANO BY 100 GIVING WRESTO REMAINDER WRESTO
               IF WRESTO > ZEROS
                   GO TO BISSEXTO
               ELSE
                   GO TO NOTBISSEXTO.
      * DIVIDIR O ANO POR 400 O RESTO DEVE SER 0 PARA SER BISSEXTO
       DIV400.
           DIVIDE WANO BY 400 GIVING WRESTO REMAINDER WRESTO
               IF WRESTO = ZEROS
                   GO TO BISSEXTO
               ELSE
                   GO TO NOTBISSEXTO.
      * SE O ANO E BISSEXTO
       BISSEXTO.
           IF WDIA > 29 OR WDIA < 1
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-ERRO
           ELSE
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-FIM.
      * SE O ANO NAO E BISSEXTO
       NOTBISSEXTO.
           IF WDIA > 28 OR WDIA < 1
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-ERRO
           ELSE
               GO TO VALDATCOMPRA-FIM.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * SE WFLAGDAT = 1 ESTAMOS VALIDANDO A DATA DE COMPRA
      * SE WFLAGDAT = 2 ESTAMOS VALIDANDO A DATA DE ULTIMO USO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       VALDATCOMPRA-ERRO.
           IF WFLAGDAT = 1
               MOVE "* DATA INVALIDA *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-011
           ELSE
               MOVE "* DATA INVALIDA *" TO MENS
               PERFORM ROT-MENS THRU ROT-MENS-FIM
               GO TO INC-012.
       VALDATCOMPRA-FIM.
           IF WFLAGDAT = 1
               GO TO INC-011FIM
           ELSE
               GO TO INC-012FIM.
